坐鳩硬 唔知有冇命出返黎啦"},{"pid":"74d6d4cf5311d12ec950c6b03aa1c453bb7d2363","tid":480182,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:08:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>個呀伯坐硬啦 連個官都玩</blockquote><br />\n即係唔玩個官就唔洗坐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪一定唔係黑就白呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你錯喇，佢嗰句明顯地暗示個阿伯要坐既其中一個原因，係因為個阿伯玩個官<br />\n<br />\n如果佢唔係咁既意思，咁佢嗰句係咪等於廢話呢？</blockquote><br />\n咁又係 佢呆唔呆都坐架啦"},{"pid":"48329bbf5bf84bd01fdc7cf472a3e72be0a3cee2","tid":480182,"uid":95,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:09:13.000Z","msg":"戇鳩廢老，唔係以為扮瞓著就唔洗坐呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1ade9a4f8cdcb13d2f9dcacfb7bec07596661ae","tid":480182,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:10:17.000Z","msg":"一死死兩件<br />\n<br />\n好波"},{"pid":"0b142fb3457fe73149af0cbcf81bca7baa8d2c1a","tid":480182,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:12:39.000Z","msg":"唔答辯，當認罪<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849dceb93694503c3214a87c4a96738c13ced241","tid":480182,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:12:55.000Z","msg":"扮晒神智不清？"},{"pid":"8634cc83c6a8cad9c4a4d937c59cb783f87ccccb","tid":480182,"uid":22349,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:18:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 廢老好暴力"},{"pid":"9b757f64cd65012efa7c4a4bf3aa0de0c5f57a9e","tid":480182,"uid":38216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T02:24:04.000Z","msg":"廢老，真係廢"},{"pid":"e52bb8c73b43754a9dac4f98d2582f651021322c","tid":480182,"uid":62815,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"ci